WEBVTT

00:03.482 --> 00:06.048
Guard: Turn around.
Take your pants off for me.

00:10.394 --> 00:13.000
Pull your underpants
down for me.

00:16.376 --> 00:17.911
Turn around.

00:19.949 --> 00:22.821
Now, bend over.

00:22.823 --> 00:25.692
All right-- get up.

00:25.694 --> 00:27.959
Turn back around.

00:27.961 --> 00:31.566
We're moving to
the holding cell.

00:39.975 --> 00:43.144
Man: Uh, these are
for you, Daniel.

00:45.414 --> 00:48.317
I'm supposed to take
your prison clothes.

