46:03.980 --> 46:06.915
Sir, you know, every second that
you could let us out early

46:06.917 --> 46:09.518
would really increase our
chances of survival.

46:09.520 --> 46:11.720
Just like our sergeant told
us before one trip into

46:11.722 --> 46:14.890
the jungle-- "men!"

46:14.892 --> 46:15.891
"Fifty of you are leavin'

46:15.893 --> 46:17.393
on a mission.

46:17.395 --> 46:19.495
